# Walkthrough: Automated Outreach & Lead Intelligence

This walkthrough demonstrates the implementation of the AI-driven Outreach and Lead Intelligence system for **Agencia B2B**.

## 🚀 Key Achievements

### 1. Premium Outreach Dashboard
A dedicated, high-performance dashboard for managing cold outreach campaigns with real-time analytics.
- **Conversion Funnel**: Visual tracking from Leads -> Contacted -> Qualified -> Won.
- **Campaign Management**: Overview of active, draft, and completed campaigns.
- **Micro-interactions**: Glassmorphic stats cards and animated progress indicators.

### 2. Intelligent Lead Enrollment
Integrated bulk actions in the [LeadsDataTable](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/src/components/admin/LeadsDataTable.tsx#173-887) allow for seamless enrollment of high-potential leads into outreach sequences.
- **Multi-selection**: Checkbox-based lead selection with global "Select All" functionality.
- **Floating Bulk Actions Bar**: A sleek, sticky action bar that appears when leads are selected.
- **Enrollment Modal**: Campaign selection and enrollment summary with impact estimation.

### 3. AI Lead Scoring & Personalization
Every lead is analyzed using an AI intelligence engine to determine their "Digital Gap" and "Opportunity Score".
- **Dynamic Tiering**: Leads are categorized as HOT, WARM, COOL, or COLD.
- **Automatic Message Generation**: Personalized WhatsApp and Email templates generated based on lead-specific problems.

## 🛠️ Technical Implementation

### Database Schema (Prisma)
New models added to [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/fmonf/Desktop/Software%20Enginnering%20LAPTOP/Agencia%20B2B/agencia-web-b2b/prisma/schema.prisma) to support complex outreach workflows:
- `OutreachCampaign`: Stores metadata, channel, and overall campaign status.
- `OutreachCampaignLead`: Connects leads to campaigns with status tracking (ENROLLED, SENT, REPLIED, etc.).
- `OutreachMessage`: Tracks every communication attempt and response.

### API Infrastructure
Standardized Next.js API routes for high-performance data retrieval:
- `GET /api/outreach/stats`: Aggregated metrics for the dashboard.
- `GET /api/outreach/campaigns`: Multi-tenant campaign listing.
- `POST /api/outreach/campaigns/[id]/enroll`: Bulk lead enrollment logic.

## 📸 Core Components

### Outreach Dashboard
Located at `/admin/outreach`. It providing a command-center view of all outreach activities.

### New Campaign Wizard
Found at `/admin/outreach/new`. A step-by-step process for launching new sequences.

### Bulk Actions Integration
Integrated directly into the Lead Management view at `/admin/dashboard`.

---

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The system is fully integrated with the multi-tenant architecture, ensuring each agency only sees and manages their own campaigns and leads.

> [!TIP]
> Use the **Opportunity Score** filter in the Lead Management table to identify the best candidates for your next outreach campaign.
